Pentax K1000</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Pentax_K1000_lens_off.jpg" class="image" title="Without lens, showing the K mount and mirror."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/Pentax_K1000_lens_off.jpg/180px-Pentax_K1000_lens_off.jpg" width="180" height="124" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
